#####Case############################

#17-case (basic transitive clauses)
Source: b:7, Mohammad A. Mohammad, attested
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {case}
qabala	 	    alwaladu      		alarnaba
qabal-a	 	    al-walad-u      	al-arnab-a
met-3sg.m		the-boy-nom         the-rabbit-acc
'The boy met the rabbit.'

#17-case (basic transitive clauses) indefinite NPs, V must be sentence-initial
Source: b:7, Mohammad A. Mohammad, attested
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {case}
qabala	 	    waladu      	arnaba
qabal-a	 	    walad-u      	arnab-a
met-3sg.m		boy-nom     rabbit-acc
'A boy met a rabbit.'


